items.title: Awesome Roadmaps
items.content_text: ### Programming Language * [PHP Developer roadmap (⭐3.7k)](https://github.com/thecodeholic/php-developer-roadmap) - Following this path will guarantee to Become a PHP Developer in 2021 [](https://github.com/thecodeholic/php-developer-roadmap) [](https://github.com/thecodeholic/php-developer-roadmap). ### Web Development * [Angular Developer Roadmap (⭐947)](https://github.com/sulco/angular-developer-roadmap) - Roadmap to becoming an Angular developer [](https://github.com/sulco/angular-developer-roadmap). * [Developer Roadmap (⭐331k)](https://github.com/kamranahmedse/developer-roadmap) - Community driven roadmaps, articles and resources for developers [](https://github.com/kamranahmedse/developer-roadmap). * [Vue Developer Roadmap (⭐530)](https://github.com/flaviocopes/vue-developer-roadmap) - Roadmap to becoming a Vue.js developer in 2019 [](https://github.com/flaviocopes/vue-developer-roadmap). ### Mobile Development * [iOS Developer Roadmap (⭐6.4k)](https://github.com/BohdanOrlov/iOS-Developer-Roadmap) - Roadmap to becoming an iOS developer in 2020 [](https://github.com/BohdanOrlov/iOS-Developer-Roadmap). ### Game Development * [Game Developer Roadmap (⭐5.7k)](https://github.com/utilForever/game-developer-roadmap) - Roadmap to becoming a game developer in 2022 [](https://github.com/utilForever/game-developer-roadmap). ### AI / Machine Learning / Data Science * [Data Engineer Roadmap (⭐13k)](https://github.com/datastacktv/data-engineer-roadmap) - Roadmap to becoming a data engineer in 2021 [](https://github.com/datastacktv/data-engineer-roadmap). * [NLP Roadmap (⭐3.3k)](https://github.com/graykode/nlp-roadmap) - Roadmap for Natural Language Processing learning in 2019 [](https://github.com/graykode/nlp-roadmap). ### Miscellaneous * [UI/UX Designer Roadmap (⭐2.2k)](https://github.com/togiberlin/ui-ux-designer-roadmap) - Roadmap on becoming a UI/UX designer in 2017 [](https://github.com/togiberlin/ui-ux-designer-roadmap).
